# Project Overview and Structure

- Single Next.js app (App Router, Next 15). Prefer Server Components and SSR by default.
- UI via shadcn/ui and Tailwind CSS v4. Composition over deep prop drilling.
- Strong TypeScript typing; avoid `any` entirely.
- Package manager is Bun; use Bun for all commands and installs.

Key configs:
- [`package.json`](mdc:package.json)
- [`tsconfig.json`](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- [`biome.json`](mdc:biome.json)

Core directories:
- `app/` — routes, layouts, server actions, and Server Components by default
- `components/` — UI components (prefer shadcn/ui primitives and Tailwind)
- `lib/` — utilities, schemas, helper modules

Import alias:
- Use `@/*` for absolute imports (see `compilerOptions.paths` in [`tsconfig.json`](mdc:tsconfig.json)).

